messages.content: Hi! How can I help you today?

Hello! I recently moved to a new house on Elm Avenue in Houston, and I have a couple of things I need help with. I have an order that was sent to my old address, and I want to change the delivery address for that order to my new home. Also, I want to update my user default address to the new home as well. Could you please look up my orders and help me with these address changes? I prefer not to disclose my address details directly. After that, I would like to exchange a tablet I bought for the cheapest one available due to moving costs.
